Kwara state government has embarked on the construction of isolation centers for victims of Lassa fever at Sobi Specialist hospital in Ilorin. Speaking during his visit to the site of the facility in Ilorin on Thursday, the commissioner for Health, Dr. Raji Razak, also directed rapid response team in the state Ministry of Health to embark on aggressive public enlightenment and training of health workers across the state on prevention of Lassa fever epidemic. ALSO READ: US to restrict visas for pregnant women Lassa fever: Oyo govt cautions against bushmeat consumption,… Christians have become endangered species in Nigeria ― CAN Killing of Journalist: Shi’ites deny attacking police BREAKING: FG reverses self on Amotekun Dr. Razak, who said that all hands must be on deck to prevent the outbreak of the infection in the state, directed the contractor in charge of the project to speed up the construction work. The commissioner explained that an alternative facility has been put in place to serve as a temporary centre before the completion of the project. Also speaking, the Director of Public Health in the state, Dr. Oluwatosin Fakayode, said the isolation center is first of its kind in North Central zone of Nigeria. Dr. Fakayode also advised residents of the state to report any suspected case of Lassa fever to the nearest health facility in the state for prompt action. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! STAY STRONGER, LONGER AND SATISFY MADAM LIKE NEVER BEFORE WITH THIS NATURAL SUPPLEMENTS WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS. CLICK NOW. CLICK HERE NOW TO WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR SPECIFIED BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS ABSOLUTELY FREE. PREMATURE EJACULATION, SMALL SIZE FINALLY CURED NATURALLY IN 2 WEEKS FOR BIGGER, LONGER, HARDER SEXIER SEX WITH NEW MAN MACHINE